The root cause is clear. The <script> tag has no defer or load guarantee — it runs immediately after the <script src> tags but the UMD bundles from unpkg may not have finished loading yet in some browsers/environments, causing React is not defined. The fix is to wrap all app code in a window.onload callback (or use defer on the CDN scripts) and also replace all "RecordLink" / "Record Link" labels with "Record Share".


